how to use Github for create a Theme==============================
   1. At frist install git -> sudo apt-get install git
   2. Username and Email Thik korte hobe->
      git config --global user.name "shahin"
      git config --global user.email "shahinmohammad24rb@gmail.com"
   3. User name and Email ta ki dilam ta cheak korar jonno-> git config --list
   4. Kono repository  k control e ante chaile oi directory te jete hobe. 
       open terminal and ->
   ->  pwd [ dia right path ase kina dekte hobe.]
   ->git init [if have a folder] or
   ->git init gitrepo.git [if not have a folder. its create a folder]
   -> ls -al [for looking .git . it called git init is working]
   5. git er sobfile asce ki na ta  dekhar jonno 
     -> git status [It make sure for coming file, Its red now]

  6.File Permision thik kora[58 min]
    we konw wp file permission is file->644=14
    we know folder/direcotry permission is = 755=17
       ---Group and username change korar jono
         ->sudo chown www newuser name:Newgroupname /link path -R [cahnge user and group owenership, R= recersive babar baba  ]

      ->sudo find /var/www . -type d -exec chomd 755 {} + [cahnge d = directory permison ,Find er por kon path  theke Find korbe ta dehay dite hobe]
      -> sudo find /var/www. -type f -exec chomd 644 {} + [super user do dia dhukte hobe, find er por file path pao dite hobe jekhan thke change hobe, f= file  ]
    7. 
    -> git add . [akhane sob kaj ses korar por file gula add kore dite hobe, ata frist kaj korar por]
    ->git add filename [prothom bar add korar por 2nd bar git add kore file name dite hobe]
  8. save kora with message by git commit
     -> git commit -m "write massage " [comment soho ]

     ==============akshte add and commit kora
     ---> git commit -a -m "comment here"[2nd time kaj koror ]

9. ->git log [comment dekhar jonno]

10. How to upload in github
     git commit chara kono bisoy taka jabe na

   -> git remote add origin [your github project link https://github.com/ShahinMohammad/Wordpress-Theme-Aptcoder-.git] or
     ->git clon in my repository and go in to .git folder. Then final push.
       
   ->git push -u origin master [Main command for upload in  github]


------------------Here use git Branch----------------
Branch create
  ->How to checek Brance 
       ->git branch
create branch
      --> git branch name [Example git branch bootstrap]

===Branch Delete====

  --->git branch -d branch_name

#How to checkout or switch branch to other branch
     -- git checkout branceName[Example git checkout Bootstrap,,,, For Master to 
          Bootstrap] 
=========Git merge korar niom==========
* jake merge korbo tar modde uncommited kono file rakha jabe na. commit kore rakte hobe
*jar shate merge korbo tar moddde jete hobe [--->git checkout fileName]
*Akhon merge korar time chole asbe
   ----->git merge jekeMergeKorbo




 

  




